data.description: Lovely home in a quiet Meeker Heights. Everything about this home feels spacious! From the open layout to the spacious bedrooms. The large primary bedroom boasts a extra large en suite with pantry cabinet, soaking tub and separate Jack & Jill sinks so everyone has their own space. The kitchen is a chefs dream featuring a center island, walk in pantry and tons of counterspace and so much storage! The skylights in the kitchen bring in lots of natural light. The property itself is spectacular with multiple outbuildings for all your toys and outdoor storage and the home sits at the top of the property with partial views out to Columbia River. Imagine sitting on the covered front porch looking out to the river valley.
